lines.line: Every day feels the same when you're alone with your thoughts.
The world outside seems so big and scary sometimes.
You find yourself hiding away, wondering if things will ever change.
Then one day, someone new comes into your life.
At first, you're not sure what to make of this unexpected friendship.
But soon you discover the joy of simply being together.
Life becomes full of playful moments and new adventures.
And you realize that sometimes the best thing in life is finding someone who makes you feel less alone in this big world.
